&lt;h2 id="the-story-of-franklin-pierce-berry"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The Story of Franklin Pierce Berry&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;a class="anchor" href="#the-story-of-franklin-pierce-berry"&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;figure class="img-float img-float-left"&gt;
 &lt;img src="https://berrytree.org/images/frankpberryky.jpg" alt="Portrait of Franklin Pierce Berry" /&gt;
&lt;/figure&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Franklin Pierce Berry&lt;/strong&gt; was born on July 12th, 1854 in Uniontown Kentucky and died on January 1st, 1909 in Williamson Co., Illinois. &lt;!-- UNSOURCED --&gt;
On February 6th, 1878 Franklin P. Berry married &lt;strong&gt;Sophia M. Sellers&lt;/strong&gt; in Evansville, Indiana. Sophie was the daughter of Orman Sellers and Louisa Ashby. She was born on April 6th, 1860 in Anton, Kentucky, and died in 1912. &lt;!-- UNSOURCED --&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Kate Berry</title><link>https://berrytree.org/ancestors/kateberryky/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://berrytree.org/ancestors/kateberryky/</guid><description>&lt;div class="ancestor-page"&gt;

